---
interface Props {}
---

<section id="stand-together" class="py-16 md:py-20 lg:py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1200px] px-6">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-10 lg:flex-row lg:gap-16">
      <!-- Text -->
      <div class="lg:w-[55%]" data-animate="slide-left">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-[clamp(24px,3.5vw,32px)] font-medium leading-tight text-text-heading">
          We Stand Together
        </h2>
        <div class="mt-6 space-y-5">
          <p class="font-body text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-text-body md:text-base">
            Addressing antisemitism is not about responding from a place of isolation or fear—it's about collective responsibility, shared learning, and unwavering support. Through dialogue, storytelling, and community care, we create spaces where people feel safe, heard, and empowered. Together, we can respond with both courage and compassion, building a future rooted in understanding and mutual respect.
          </p>
          <p class="font-body text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-text-body md:text-base">
            Whether you're seeking resources for yourself, your family, or your community, Jewmanity is here to walk alongside you with tools, guidance, and connection.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Image placeholder -->
      <div class="lg:w-[45%]" data-animate="slide-right">
        <img src="/images/sections/heads-up-safe-haven.jpg" alt="Community standing together against antisemitism" class="aspect-[4/3] w-full rounded-2xl object-cover" width="600" height="400" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
